potential for M&A) and could use some counsel. Let me know if you have time
for a conversation in the next week or two!!*
It looks like the world is starting to heat up again, what with two highly
effective vaccine candidates and a new US president who doesn't appear to
be a fascist. Here's where I'm at with my three main targets:

1. Contracting: I've got a couple conversations going with
