positioning!

3. CGM Project: I've officially parked this until Q2 2021, because of the
above.

I hope that, wherever you are, you and yours are well and healthy. These
are crazy, heady times. Let's harness the change!

All best wishes,
Josh

P.S. *BONUS*: My media outreach protocol ("*How to automate meaningful
